tip.text: Picolo latte still my favourite here. Nice giant wood tables that really get ya comfy for chit chat. Milo fudge cake's great.. But don really get the milo thing. A great choc fudge cake!
Yet another satisfying meal!!! This time top score to a mini sized seafood paella individually cooked on skillet and Baked bone marrow. Done in a way that's tasty and not foul. Fries v fresh!
Go for lunch! Easier to get a seat. Madagascar prawn gambas, scallop cerviche highly recommended! Everything else is great too.. Including chef andrew! =) overall gd svc, nice setting and gd food!
